01:15.625 --> 01:16.785
♪ Bills pile up ♪

01:17.666 --> 01:18.786
♪ Sky high ♪

01:20.291 --> 01:22.081
♪ Send that boy off ♪

01:22.750 --> 01:24.040
♪ To die... ♪

