[Angela Davis]  If the link-up is not made

01:26.291 --> 01:29.581
between what's happening
in Vietnam and here,

01:29.666 --> 01:35.416
we may very well face a period
of full-blown fascism very soon.

01:35.500 --> 01:36.880
♪ Crime is ♪

01:37.666 --> 01:39.076
♪ Increasing ♪

01:40.583 --> 01:42.133
♪ Trigger-happy ♪

01:42.833 --> 01:44.133
♪ Policing ♪

01:45.791 --> 01:46.961
♪ Panic ♪

01:48.208 --> 01:49.208
♪ Is spreading ♪

01:50.916 --> 01:51.746
