01:51.833 --> 01:54.423
[Lyndon B. Johnson]  I shall not seek
and I will not accept

01:54.916 --> 01:58.166
the nomination of my party
for another term as your president.

02:01.666 --> 02:02.576
[gunshot echoes]

02:06.500 --> 02:12.630
[Richard Nixon]  America needs a full-time
president and a full-time Congress.

02:12.708 --> 02:15.628
I shall resign the presidency
effective at noon tomorrow.

02:15.708 --> 02:19.998
[Bobby Seale]  In the Civil War, 186,000
black men fought in the military service,

02:20.083 --> 02:23.333
and we were promised freedom
and we didn't get it. In World War II,

02:23.416 --> 02:26.206
850,000 black men fought,
and we were promised freedom,

02:26.291 --> 02:29.381
and we didn't get it. Now here we go
with the damn Vietnam War,

02:29.458 --> 02:32.918
and we still ain't gettin' nothin'
but racist police brutality, et cetera.

02:33.000 --> 02:36.880
♪ Mother, mother ♪

02:37.791 --> 02:39.001
♪ Mother, mother ♪

02:40.583 --> 02:43.133
♪ Everybody thinks we're wrong ♪

02:43.208 --> 02:44.628
♪ Mother, mother ♪

02:45.166 --> 02:47.956
♪ Who are they to judge us? ♪

02:48.041 --> 02:50.331
♪ Mother, mother... ♪

02:51.083 --> 02:52.793
[song fading]

02:52.875 --> 02:54.245
[indistinct chatter]

02:56.583 --> 03:00.173
God damn! Whoo!

03:00.250 --> 03:02.540
