Let me give you some power.

03:28.791 --> 03:31.631
-Let me see if I can remember this.
-Come on, you got it.

03:32.750 --> 03:35.670
-Okay, all right. Here we go.
-Give me some of that black shit.

03:35.750 --> 03:37.500
[all exclaiming]

03:39.333 --> 03:40.753
-Get in here.
-Oh!

03:40.833 --> 03:43.383
-Finally. Finally.
-Oh!

03:43.458 --> 03:44.708
-Yeah, man.
-Look at you.

03:44.791 --> 03:47.131
-How you doing?
-I'm all right. I'm all right.

03:47.208 --> 03:48.918
-Bring it here!
-There he is.

03:49.666 --> 03:50.826
How we feelin'?

03:50.916 --> 03:52.286
[all laughing]

03:54.041 --> 03:56.581
-Hold on.
-Finally. Finally.

03:56.666 --> 03:58.206
Now, look at you.

03:58.791 --> 04:01.961
-It sure is good to see y'all.
-Ain't this some shit?

04:02.041 --> 04:05.251
I'm tellin', it's a stone cold trip
being back here in country.

04:05.333 --> 04:09.213
Baby, we got off that plane, that heat
hit me upside the head, ski-bop!

04:09.291 --> 04:10.541
Just like in '68.

04:10.625 --> 04:14.625
-Yeah, brother man, we are back.
-The Bloods is back.

04:14.708 --> 04:18.668
-5 Bloods don't die, we just multiply!
-Yeah, yeah!

04:18.750 --> 04:20.250
Soon to be five.

04:22.708 --> 04:23.578
-Amen.
-Amen.

04:28.208 --> 04:31.038
Hey, uh, look what I found.

04:32.291 --> 04:34.251
[man 1]  Oh. Young Blood.

04:34.333 --> 04:36.213
-[man 2]  Get you home, Blood.
-[man 1]  Damn.

04:36.291 --> 04:37.881
Brother man in all his glory.

04:37.958 --> 04:39.538
-Amen.
-Let me see it, man.

04:42.208 --> 04:43.708
Mmm-mmm-mmm.

04:44.541 --> 04:46.381
-Uh, ma'am?
-[receptionist] Yes, sir.

04:46.458 --> 04:50.378
Can you please make sure
that all four rooms are on my card?

04:50.458 --> 04:52.248
No, no, thank you. I'm good. I'm good.

04:52.333 --> 04:54.333
-[Eddie] Hey, on me, remember?
-Nah, nah, I got mine.

04:54.416 --> 04:58.126
-I ain't your welfare charity case.
-Ain't nobody saying no shit like that.

04:58.208 --> 05:01.538
Everybody know your black ass
and that big black Amex card,

05:01.625 --> 05:04.915
