05:05.000 --> 05:06.750
Keep your money, man.

05:06.833 --> 05:08.423
I see your head still hard as hell.

05:08.500 --> 05:10.080
Just like my Swanson Johnson.

05:10.166 --> 05:11.036
[all laughing]

05:11.125 --> 05:13.415
Man, you crazy as hell, bruh.

05:14.875 --> 05:16.875
["Got To Give It Up"
