[exclaiming]

06:09.375 --> 06:12.705
♪ I done got myself together, baby ♪

06:12.791 --> 06:14.501
♪ I'm havin' a ball ♪

06:14.583 --> 06:15.883
[all chuckling]

06:18.416 --> 06:21.126
Hey, y'all know I got an 18-year-old son?

06:21.208 --> 06:22.248
What, he's 18 now?

06:22.333 --> 06:23.543
Yeah, check this out.

06:24.500 --> 06:26.500
-Huh?
-Look at that handsome dude, man.

06:26.583 --> 06:27.543
Yeah.

06:27.625 --> 06:30.705
-Must take after his mama.
-[all laugh]

06:30.791 --> 06:33.711
I got thug-ass hardheads
moving into my hood.

06:33.791 --> 06:35.581
