45:54.666 --> 45:56.456
[Eddie] Man, it's just a goddamn chicken.

45:56.541 --> 45:58.291
[seller in Vietnamese]

45:58.375 --> 45:59.875
[in English]

45:59.958 --> 46:01.328
Huh? What?

46:02.375 --> 46:04.165
[overlapping shouts]

46:04.250 --> 46:06.420
You don't know nothing about me, man!
Fuck that!

46:06.500 --> 46:08.290
[in Vietnamese]

46:08.375 --> 46:09.665
[Paul] You don't know shit about me!

46:09.750 --> 46:12.540
I didn't kill your mother and father!
Fuck you!

46:12.625 --> 46:14.535
-[Vinh speaking Vietnamese]
-[Paul] You don't know me!

46:14.625 --> 46:15.575
[David] Let's go. Come on.

46:15.666 --> 46:17.666
You don't know what the fuck
