46:17.750 --> 46:20.250
-[Vinh speaking Vietnamese]
-[Paul] What the fuck you know about me?

46:20.875 --> 46:23.455
-[speaking English]
-Paul, relax!

46:23.541 --> 46:25.541
-Man, nah! He kept coming up on me!
-[speaking Vietnamese]

46:25.625 --> 46:27.625
