-What the fuck?

46:27.708 --> 46:29.788
-[speaking Vietnamese]
-[Paul] What the fuck is going down?

46:29.875 --> 46:32.245
-I got you. I got you, brother.
-[seller speaking Vietnamese]

46:32.333 --> 46:33.503
Stop talking, and fuck you!

46:33.583 --> 46:35.213
-Get the boat moving!
-Move on, man!

46:35.291 --> 46:37.041
-I got you.
-Stop fucking talking!

46:37.125 --> 46:39.875
-Don't know shit about me.
-You killed my father and mother!

46:39.958 --> 46:41.038
What are you doing?

46:41.125 --> 46:42.915
He knows what "gook" means, man!

46:43.000 --> 46:44.540
I don't give a fuck about that!

46:44.625 --> 46:47.745
I don't give two fucks about that.
I tried to talk to the man.

46:47.833 --> 46:50.753
-[speaking Vietnamese]
-[Paul] Put the fucking camera down.

46:50.833 --> 46:53.833
You're just having a panic attack.
This shit happen to you all the time?

46:54.333 --> 46:56.333
-Yeah, he has PTSD.
-This happen all the time?

46:56.416 --> 46:57.576
-He gets triggered.
-Come on.

46:57.666 --> 46:59.626
[David] The guy off with his shit.
It be all right.

46:59.708 --> 47:02.538
Hey, David. What you know about it, huh?

47:02.625 --> 47:04.325
You don't know nothin' about this.

47:04.958 --> 47:08.038
-I don't have no fucking--
-Nightmares. You been having nightmares.

47:08.125 --> 47:09.875
-He does.
-I don't have no nightmares.

47:09.958 --> 47:11.248
-[David] You do.
-[Eddie] We all got PTSD.

47:11.333 --> 47:13.503
-[Paul] Come on and tell me. Look.
-Just breathe, come on.

47:13.583 --> 47:14.463
I see...

47:15.541 --> 47:16.751
-Come on.
-I...

47:16.833 --> 47:21.293
Come on, bud. Come on.
There you go. There you go.

47:22.125 --> 47:24.125
-Come on.
-I see ghosts, y'all. [voice breaks]

47:24.833 --> 47:25.963
I see...

47:28.208 --> 47:29.038
ghosts.

47:29.125 --> 47:31.035
Well, it happens to all of us, man!

47:31.125 --> 47:32.705
-You seen 'em, too?
-Yeah.

47:33.208 --> 47:35.538
Dead come to you at night? Huh?

47:36.666 --> 47:39.246
Stormin' Norm comes to me
damn near every night.

47:39.333 --> 47:42.083
Now, he talk to y'all like he talk to me?

47:42.166 --> 47:44.376
-[Otis] Brother, come on.
-I don't think so.

47:44.458 --> 47:46.078
Come on. Come on.

47:46.166 --> 47:47.956
-Take it easy, man.
-Go ahead, get it out.

47:48.041 --> 47:49.631
-Yeah.
-Get it out. Come on now.

47:50.208 --> 47:52.458
-Come on, bud.
-Think I'm a crazy fuck, don't you?

47:52.541 --> 47:53.631
No!

47:53.708 --> 47:54.998
-[Eddie] Come on, man.
-Smart niggas, huh?

47:55.083 --> 47:57.083
-[Otis] It ain't like that.
-Man, don't call me that.

47:57.166 --> 48:00.036
That's right. Y'all saditty niggas
don't like that word.

48:00.125 --> 48:02.915
You know what, man? Nigga. Nigga.

48:03.000 --> 48:07.790
Nigga. Nigga. Nigga! [chuckles]
A yellow nigga.

48:07.875 --> 48:08.785
-[Eddie] What?
-You feel me?

48:08.875 --> 48:11.745
Look, I'm tired of this bullshit!
Squash it!

48:12.916 --> 48:15.666
I'm with you. I'm with you.

48:18.416 --> 48:19.246
Fists up!

48:24.833 --> 48:27.883
Get in there, David. Get in there.
Put your fist up, David.

48:29.458 --> 48:30.288
Come on.

48:31.083 --> 48:35.043
You, too, Vinh. Go ahead! Fist up, man.

48:35.541 --> 48:36.581
Come on, Paul.

48:40.958 --> 48:44.998
-Bloods!
-Norm! Norm!

49:21.583 --> 49:23.083
-Get that out of my face.
-[Eddie laughs]

49:23.166 --> 49:23.996
Get that out of my face.

49:33.208 --> 49:35.208
[indistinct conversation in Vietnamese]

49:36.708 --> 49:38.498
[man in English] And I told him,
"Pick your poison,"

49:38.583 --> 49:40.833
and he told the waitress
to pick the poison.

49:41.500 --> 49:42.420
-Excuse me.
-Sorry.

49:43.291 --> 49:44.921
-[man] How's it going, boss?
-[David] How you doin'?

49:45.000 --> 49:46.330
[man] I'll be better at the bar.

49:53.125 --> 49:55.285
[David] Didn't think I'd meet
another American here.

49:59.666 --> 50:01.206
But I'm French. [chuckles]

50:01.291 --> 50:03.131
-Beg your pardon?
-I'm French.

50:04.125 --> 50:04.955
Sit.

50:07.375 --> 50:08.875
You're traveling alone?

50:09.583 --> 50:11.963
I'm here with a group of Vietnam vets.

50:13.291 --> 50:14.541
One is my father.

50:16.166 --> 50:18.126
Must be something powerful,

50:18.208 --> 50:20.668
coming back after all these years
with your father.

50:21.250 --> 50:22.880
-Yeah, it's powerful all right.
-Yeah.

50:24.166 --> 50:25.076
What is your name?

50:25.666 --> 50:30.376
Hedy. Like Hedy Lamarr. No?

50:30.458 --> 50:32.668
Old time Hollywood star.

50:33.875 --> 50:36.375
But, well, my last name is Bouvier, so...

50:37.833 --> 50:38.673
Cool.

50:39.375 --> 50:40.245
It's cool.

50:41.416 --> 50:44.706
-Uh, I'm David.
-Ah, David from the Bible.

50:45.250 --> 50:48.630
-Like David Ruffin from the Temptations.
-[Hedy chuckles]

50:49.375 --> 50:50.455
Motown.

50:52.166 --> 50:53.326
Yeah, you got it.

50:56.708 --> 50:59.168
Is there another place
to go at night around here?

50:59.250 --> 51:02.000
["Time Has Come Today"
by The Chambers Brothers playing]

51:08.000 --> 51:10.000
[indistinct chatter]

51:14.125 --> 51:17.075
Have you ever seen
so many scooters in your life? [chuckles]

51:20.208 --> 51:21.038
Thank you.

51:21.125 --> 51:21.995
[waitress in Vietnamese]

51:23.916 --> 51:24.956
So...

51:27.416 --> 51:28.786
what's their story?

51:29.375 --> 51:32.495
Well, Simon is my best friend.

51:33.708 --> 51:38.288
And Seppo and I use each other for sex
once in a blue moon.

51:39.291 --> 51:44.751
What do you, Simon and Sep... Seppo...
Seppo... what do you do?

51:44.833 --> 51:49.383
We locate old landmines,
and detonate bombs, too.

51:49.458 --> 51:50.498
Wow!

51:51.541 --> 51:53.171
-Wow, okay.
-"Wow, okay!" [laughs]

51:53.250 --> 51:55.460
Yeah, that's some gangster shit. For sure!

51:56.250 --> 52:01.000
How does one get involved in
the landmine disposal business? Pray tell.

52:01.833 --> 52:04.503
The Bouviers have a history in Vietnam.

52:06.083 --> 52:09.503
It's strange how a war never ends
for those involved.

52:09.583 --> 52:12.923
See, like, landmines planted years ago...

52:13.833 --> 52:17.173
and still harvesting death
all these years later.

52:17.583 --> 52:19.173
Back to your family history.

52:19.666 --> 52:24.996
My family made several fortunes
owning a rubber plantation,

52:25.875 --> 52:30.125
and then they bought up much more of
the rice market and made another fortune.

52:30.208 --> 52:31.748
See, the white gold.

52:33.541 --> 52:34.421
Hmm.

52:36.208 --> 52:37.788
Wonderful family business.

52:38.916 --> 52:42.666
But one exception, we exploited
the shit out of the Vietnamese people.

52:43.500 --> 52:45.630
So, that's the meaning behind the mines.

52:46.291 --> 52:49.041
So, what did the Bouvier family
think about what you do?

52:49.125 --> 52:50.375
[chuckles] What family?

52:53.708 --> 52:59.628
I'm the founder and the director of LAMB,
which I started three years ago.

52:59.708 --> 53:00.538
LAMB?

53:00.625 --> 53:04.575
Yeah, LAMB. Love Against Mines and Bombs.

53:08.083 --> 53:12.753
[laughs] No. I must look like
some Patty Hearst heiress

53:12.833 --> 53:17.543
who's cast herself
as a guilt-ridden bourgeoisie cliché.

53:18.041 --> 53:20.671
Hey, look,
I know all about bourgeoisie clichés.

53:21.500 --> 53:24.920
I'm a poverty-stricken fool
who loves teaching kids.

53:25.500 --> 53:28.290
However, my guilt trip
is a lot less dangerous than yours.

53:28.375 --> 53:29.825
-Yeah, less dangerous.
-Yeah.

53:29.916 --> 53:32.126
-[Hedy laughing]
-Unless you count school shootings.

53:33.375 --> 53:35.125
School shootings. No fun.

53:37.000 --> 53:39.830
You always been the solid one, always.

53:40.541 --> 53:44.881
Got a... wife who loves you.
Daughter who loves you.

53:45.625 --> 53:48.495
You got a son who loves you enough
for two daddies.

53:48.583 --> 53:50.423
I couldn't love David...

53:53.625 --> 53:54.495
back.

53:58.583 --> 54:02.253
You got back to the world,
you made that transition.

54:03.208 --> 54:07.078
Me, I'm all... fucked up inside.

54:08.083 --> 54:09.543
I'm broken, man.

54:15.583 --> 54:16.503
Broken.

54:18.666 --> 54:21.246
-[sobs] Fuck.
-Whoa, whoa, whoa.

54:24.166 --> 54:26.916
-Blood, we're all broken.
-Not like me, man.

54:28.000 --> 54:32.330
Norm and I were holding those gooks back
when the man bought it. I see him.

54:36.208 --> 54:37.538
I saw him die, man.

54:42.791 --> 54:43.791
[Paul clears throat]

54:43.875 --> 54:46.955
-So what? You're blaming yourself?
-You don't even know.

54:52.333 --> 54:56.043
Paul, when we get back to the world,
I'd like you to come with me to a meeting.

54:56.125 --> 54:59.995
I don't do that "sit in a circle,
whine about shit" group thing, man.

55:00.083 --> 55:03.043
I don't do it.
I never have and I never will.

55:03.125 --> 55:05.375
You got to talk to somebody.

55:05.458 --> 55:09.458
I talk to my brother Stormin' Norman
every single night.

55:12.625 --> 55:14.995
[in Vietnamese]

55:17.708 --> 55:20.038
-[in English] Yeah.
-Oh, oh, oh, drink, drink.

55:20.125 --> 55:21.785
[chattering indistinctly]

55:21.875 --> 55:23.995
[in Vietnamese]

55:28.333 --> 55:29.543
Whoa.

55:33.458 --> 55:36.378
[in English] Hey. Simon.

55:38.000 --> 55:40.710
-David.
-David. Okay. How's it going?

55:40.791 --> 55:41.631
I can't call it.

55:42.625 --> 55:45.205
Hey, that dude over there by the bar,
is he with you?

55:45.291 --> 55:47.331
-He's getting pretty shit-faced.
-Uh-huh. Brotherman.

55:47.416 --> 55:49.126
[Seppo in Finnish]

55:52.166 --> 55:54.126
[in English] It's been an emotional trip.

55:54.708 --> 55:56.248
[in English] It appears so.

55:56.625 --> 55:59.825
You Americans are just
incredibly uninformed.

56:01.666 --> 56:04.206
I guess you're too busy
watching reality TV,

56:04.833 --> 56:07.883
or electing a reality TV clown
for a president.

56:07.958 --> 56:08.878
Knew that was coming.

56:08.958 --> 56:12.498
Well, on behalf of all the black folks
in the USA,

56:12.583 --> 56:15.293
which are the only group
who didn't vote for the motherfucker,

56:15.375 --> 56:19.665
we plead innocent to all charges,
claims, accusations, allegations,

56:19.750 --> 56:23.210
and associations connected to the Klansman
in the Oval Office,

56:23.291 --> 56:24.421
so help me God.

56:24.500 --> 56:26.250
[in Vietnamese]

56:27.500 --> 56:30.710
The Bloods search
for the lost treasure of youth

56:30.791 --> 56:33.791
and the remains of the dearly departed
Norman Earl Holloway...

56:33.875 --> 56:38.415
-We're going.
-...KIA, December 7th, 1971.

56:39.375 --> 56:43.575
We're here to bring home
a fallen brother. A brother!

56:44.708 --> 56:50.168
A tomb is sacred, not to be looted
by rogues and vandals.

56:50.250 --> 56:54.380
There's gold in them hills!
Gold, goddamn it, gold!

56:56.041 --> 56:58.041
[dramatic instrumental music plays]

57:00.125 --> 57:02.575
[bugs chirring, birds twittering]

57:32.666 --> 57:34.206
[Melvin] Thanks for getting us
this far, Vinh.

57:34.291 --> 57:35.131
[Vinh] My pleasure.

57:35.208 --> 57:37.828
I gotta tell you, you put on
one hell of a tour.

57:37.916 --> 57:41.536
-[Otis] Sure do. Thanks Vinhi-vin.
-[Vinh] You're welcome.

57:42.250 --> 57:47.170
Nothing is more precious than independence
and liberty. Said by our uncle.

57:47.250 --> 57:49.920
-[Otis] What uncle?
-Uncle Ho Chi Minh.

57:50.000 --> 57:51.710
-Now he's your uncle?
-[chuckles]

57:51.791 --> 57:54.791
Actually, he's the father
of modern-day Vietnam.

57:54.875 --> 57:56.415
Like your George Washington.

57:56.500 --> 58:01.290
Oh, my dear misinformed,
misguided... Thank you.

58:01.958 --> 58:03.288
...Vietnamese brother.

58:04.000 --> 58:08.250
Our Uncle George owned 123 slaves.

58:09.083 --> 58:14.003
And as they say
in our colonists' second language, touché.

58:14.583 --> 58:18.383
[Paul] Get your arms out, man.
Get your arms out. And back, too.

58:19.458 --> 58:23.668
All right, get my arms and my back, man.
What's up? Arms and back!

58:23.750 --> 58:25.130
[David] There, I got you. I got you.

58:25.208 --> 58:27.628
Bloods, I can't believe
we back up in this bitch.

58:28.791 --> 58:31.461
I'll meet you at this rendezvous location
in a few days.

58:31.541 --> 58:33.541
-All right.
-If you're late or early, don't worry.

58:33.625 --> 58:34.575
I'll be there.

58:35.125 --> 58:36.575
I hope you find your friend.

58:41.541 --> 58:42.671
Bon voyage.

58:43.166 --> 58:45.666
[all in Vietnamese]

58:46.458 --> 58:47.958
[in English] Showtime. Showtime, baby.

58:50.708 --> 58:53.828
Bloods. I'm gonna teach you that.
Y'all ready?

58:53.916 --> 58:54.916
-Yeah, let's go.
-Yeah.

58:55.000 --> 58:55.920
You got the paperwork?

58:56.000 --> 58:57.920
[Otis] You can see I got
the paperwork with me.

58:58.000 --> 59:00.080
[Melvin] Is that a MAGA hat? God damn!

59:00.166 --> 59:02.076
[Otis] Straight, straight. I got you.

59:03.833 --> 59:05.173
[Vinh in Vietnamese]

59:07.208 --> 59:09.708
